{
  "info": {
    "name": "Raag App — Course video bookmarks",
    "description": "Learner-only **`/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks`** CRUD.\n\n### Variables\n- **`baseUrl`**, **`access_token`** (user **Login** from main collection)\n- **`course_id`** — paste a real course `_id`, or use **Course** requests in the main collection\n- **`course_video_id`** — filled by **Get videos by course** (prerequisite), or paste a **CourseVideo** `_id`\n- **`course_video_bookmark_id`** — filled by **Get my bookmarks** or **Add bookmark**\n\n### Endpoints\n| Method | Path | |\n|--------|------|---|\n| GET | `/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks` | My bookmarks (paginated) |\n| POST | `/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks` | Add (`courseVideoId`, optional `note`) |\n| GET | `/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/:id` | One bookmark |\n| PUT | `/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/:id` | Update `note` |\n| DELETE | `/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/:id` | Remove |\n\nDuplicate same video → **200** + **`alreadyBookmarked`: true**. Each item includes **`courseVideo`**, **`course`**, **`userId`**, **`note`**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_video_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_video_bookmark_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Prerequisite · Get videos by course",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    const v = j.videos && j.videos[0];",
              "    if (v && v._id) pm.collectionVariables.set('course_video_id', v._id);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video/course/{{course_id}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video", "course", "{{course_id}}"]
        },
        "description": "Sets **`course_video_id`** from the first video. Set **`{{course_id}}`** first (Mongo **Course** `_id`). Optional Bearer (same token is fine)."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Get my bookmarks",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (j.bookmarks && j.bookmarks.length && j.bookmarks[0]._id) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('course_video_bookmark_id', j.bookmarks[0]._id);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks?page=1&limit=20",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
            { "key": "limit", "value": "20" }
          ]
        },
        "description": "**GET /** — Paginated list for the logged-in learner."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Add bookmark",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const j = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (j.bookmark && j.bookmark._id) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('course_video_bookmark_id', j.bookmark._id);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"courseVideoId\": \"{{course_video_id}}\",\n  \"note\": \"Watch later\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks"]
        },
        "description": "**POST /** — Requires **`{{course_video_id}}`** (run prerequisite or paste)."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Get bookmark by ID",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/{{course_video_bookmark_id}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks", "{{course_video_bookmark_id}}"]
        },
        "description": "**GET /:id** — Must be your bookmark."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Update bookmark",
      "request": {
        "method": "PUT",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"note\": \"Updated note\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/{{course_video_bookmark_id}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks", "{{course_video_bookmark_id}}"]
        },
        "description": "**PUT /:id** — Body **`note`** required (can be empty string)."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Delete bookmark",
      "request": {
        "method": "DELETE",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/course-video-bookmarks/{{course_video_bookmark_id}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "course-video-bookmarks", "{{course_video_bookmark_id}}"]
        },
        "description": "**DELETE /:id**"
      }
    }
  ]
}
